g&h=d70688d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20140228/photo/0228-00470-074p1g1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20140228%2Fphoto%2F0228-00470-074p1g1.jpg&h=1cfe69ce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"23fe9cbd8bfa9c25be59c19139c69a7faef6325e","tid":385953,"uid":111903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"哨到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3192bf15a8620ec00c1283d093fcf475826efb02","tid":385953,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:43:30.000Z","msg":"港姐2017冠軍 雷莊𠒇老豆原來係億萬富豪<br />\n<br />\n香港小姐2017終於塵埃落定，冠軍由23歲來自多倫多的雷莊𠒇，原來老豆雷葆文係香港的十大傑出設計師， 人稱「設計多面手」，而且身家十分富有，香港及海外都擁有物業，傳聞係億億聲，在商界有頭有面。雷莊𠒇曾表示父親十分支持她參選，當然佢自己都十分有料到，作為唯一嘅海外突入佳麗，身高成5呎7寸，身材更加是十分惹火，因為佢係模特兒出身㗎！"},{"pid":"a7d6f03d01aa00f4467c750684b11126c88f59b1","tid":385953,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"她又開估雷莊𠒇的「𠒇」字之謎，她說：「其實我當年攞身份證嗰陣一直冇發覺，原來喺嗰刻已經寫錯咗，到我參選，我仲問大會做乜寫錯我名，佢哋話係跟住我身份證咁寫，我先發覺寫錯咗，我遲啲會去改番！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來佢文盲"},{"pid":"cf45c7eec749d4338489360a7381c658ac62b957","tid":385953,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"Yahoo有猿人"}]}